{"vocabInfos":[{"lsjDefs":"<b> βαθμ-ός</b> <br /> or <b>βασμός</b>, ὁ, (βαίνω) <b>step, threshold,</b> [<a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" title=\" LXX.1Ki.5.5, [5th c.BC: Sophocles Tragicus] “fragment” 1127 \">LXX+5th c.BC+</a>]; <b>degree</b> on the dial, [<a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" title=\" LXX.2Ki.20.9f \">LXX</a>]; <b>fifteen degrees</b> of the zodiac, [<a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" title=\" 2nd c.AD: Vettius Valens Astrologus 31.2 \">Refs 2nd c.AD+</a>]; <b>interval</b> in a musical scale, [<a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" title=\" 4th c.AD: Iamblichus Philosophus “de vita Pythagorica” 26.120. \">Refs 4th c.AD+</a>]<br /><Level3><b>__2</b></Level3> <b>rung</b> of a ladder, [<a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" title=\" 2nd c.AD: Lucianus Sophista “Trag.” 221. \">Refs 2nd c.AD+</a>]<br /><Level3><b>__3</b></Level3> <b>base</b> or <b>plinth</b> of a tower, [<a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" title=\" “GDI” 5524.10 (from Cyzicus). \">Refs</a>]<br /><Level2><b>__II</b></Level2> <i>metaphorically</i>, <b>step, degree</b> in rank (οἱ β. κλίμακος προκοπὴν σημαίνουσι [<a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" title=\" 2nd c.AD: Artemidorus Daldianus Onirocriticus 2.42), NT.1Tim.3.13, 6th c.AD: Procopius Caesariensis Historicus “Historia Arcana” 24, 6th c.AD: Lydus, Joannes Laurentius Historicus “Mag.” 2.8, +others; οἱ τᾶς ἀξίας βάσμοι “IG” 12(2).243.16 (Mytil.)\">NT+2nd c.AD+</a>]; simply, <b>degree,</b> τολμημάτων βαθμοί [<a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" title=\" 1st c.AD: Josephus Historicus “Bellum Judaicum” 4.3.10; ὥσπερ ἡδονῆς κλίμακα συμπηξάμενος ἔρως πρῶτον ἔχει β. ὄψεως 2nd c.AD: Lucianus Sophista “Am.” 53 \">Refs 1st c.AD+</a>]; <b>step</b> in an argument, [<a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" title=\" 6th c.AD: Simplicius Philosophus “in Aristotelis de Caelo commentaria - Comm. in Arist. Graeca” 718.35 \">Refs 6th c.AD+</a>]; of a genealogy, ἀπωτέρω δυοῖν β. two <b>steps</b> farther back, i.e. farther back than one's grandfather, [<a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" title=\" 1st-2nd c.AD: Dio Chrysostomus Sophista 41.6. \">Refs 1st c.AD+</a>]<br /><Level2><b>__III</b></Level2> <b>tax paid on stairs,</b> [<a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" title=\" POxy. 574 (2nd c.AD): _accusative_ to 2nd c.AD: Phrynichus Atticista 296, 2nd c.AD: Moeris Grammaticus 97, βαθμός is _Ionic dialect_, βασμός _Attic dialect_, but βασμός occurs “GDI” 5524.10 (Cyzic.), “Jahresh.” 3.55 (from Scepsis). \">Refs 2nd c.AD+</a>]","strongNumber":"G0898","accentedUnicode":"βαθμός","relatedNos":[{"strongNumber":"G0899","matchingForm":"βάθος","stepTransliteration":"bathos","gloss":"depth","_zh_tw_Gloss":"深","_es_Gloss":"profundidad","_zh_Gloss":"深"}],"shortDef":"standing, rank","mediumDef":"standing, rank <br /><i>primarily</i> <b>a step, stair;</b> <i>metaphorically</i> <b>grade</b> of dignity, <b>degree, rank, standing,</b> <ref='1Ti.3.13'>1Tim. 3:13</ref>*","stepGloss":"standing","stepTransliteration":"bathmos","count":1,"_es_Definition":"prestigio, posición, estatus","_zh_tw_Definition":"(屬靈或聰智的進展) 階段 (多 3:13)","_zh_Definition":"(属灵或聪智的进展) 阶段 (多 3:13)","_step_Type":"word","_vi_Definition":"bậc; địa vị.","_zh_tw_Gloss":"地步","_es_Gloss":"posición","_zh_Gloss":"地步"}]}